@NODE intro "Introduction"
@{u}Introduction@{uu}

   This is a handy little door with no real use (yet?), all it does is allow
you or a user to explore the Userbase on your BBS either by just listing it,
involking a search or bringing up a statistics screen. Excuse me for ripping
the name of a certain Microshaft product but what I came out with sounded 
quite appropriate, so thats why I called it Userbase Explorer (UBE for short).

@{u}Features@{uu}

o Looks nice.
o Lots of useful information of users :).
o Search for people in the town of your choice or using the computer of your
  choice and many more seach options.
o Nice statistics screen.
o Quite useless, but a nice addition to any BBS.
o Freeware!

   Anyway, have a browse of this guide, check out all the relevant sections
and stuff, oh and don't forget to contact @{" me " LINK credits} :).

@ENDNODE

